OpenCAPWAP v1.0

DTLS:
	AC and WTP can connect using OpenSSL on Control Channel, Data Channel or both

MORE WTP, ONE IP:
	AC accepts connections from multiple WTPs with same IP and different ports

SPLIT MAC:
	OpenCAPWAP v1.0 works in SPLIT MAC mode too

ACCESS POINT:
	AC can handle one or more Access Point on its associated WTPs. Client stations can connect to WTP's Master mode interfaces.

For more info, please refer to "The new version of OpenCAPWAP", E. Agostini, M. Bernaschi, M. Vellucci, L. Vollero
Submitted to "International Journal of Network Management"
